energy.usef.dso.config

Enum ConfigDsoParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ConfigDsoParam>
      • energy.usef.dso.config.ConfigDsoParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ConfigDsoParam>

    public enum ConfigDsoParam
extends Enum<ConfigDsoParam>
    The Config DSO parameter contains all configuration parameters which can be used in distribution service operator component of USEF. The property class is used to do some validations on the parameter. Also a user defined class can be entered with user specific validations, e.g. a parameter should be integer and positive. An enumeration is used to configure the parameters to define the config parameter more type safe (before a string value was used).
